00:13:49.630 --> 00:13:52.297
I feel like I can, I don't know,
go about my business


246
00:13:52.383 --> 00:13:54.257
without looking
in every direction


247
00:13:54.343 --> 00:13:57.719
for some guy
creeping up behind me and...


248
00:13:57.763 --> 00:13:59.805
I don't know. I can just...

