00:38:12.591 --> 00:38:14.383
And b: No.

685
00:38:14.468 --> 00:38:17.845
But I think you're pushed pretty
close to your limit right now.


686
00:38:17.930 --> 00:38:21.431
Now, how have you been sleeping?

687
00:38:21.517 --> 00:38:23.433
- Not great.
- So you're tired.


